Or I can set up a task server
to do it over the weekend.

00:48:43.440 --> 00:48:49.760
Even better, if I don't wanna do that,
if I have a Mac OS X server,

00:48:49.800 --> 00:48:54.210
I can set up net install and
I can tell all the users,

00:48:54.210 --> 00:48:57.760
tomorrow morning when you come in,
after you hear the chime,

00:48:57.810 --> 00:49:01.920
just hold down the N key, the letter N,
