Mac deployment is unbelievably
extremely efficient.

00:49:53.490 --> 00:49:56.380
The support involves the
creation of the image,

00:49:56.620 --> 00:50:00.540
the testing of the image,
the deployment of the image,

00:50:00.650 --> 00:50:05.380
