00:50:15.300 --> 00:50:16.300
Play with it.

00:50:16.460 --> 00:50:18.000
Try it out.

00:50:18.450 --> 00:50:23.200
There are other tools out
there that you can use.

00:50:23.270 --> 00:50:26.900
Do your remote update planning carefully.

00:50:26.930 --> 00:50:29.310
Are you going to use
ARD with a task server?

00:50:29.450 --> 00:50:32.700
Are you going to use net
install with packages?

00:50:32.700 --> 00:50:36.290
We can build our own packages too.

00:50:36.470 --> 00:50:42.390
For example, I have an iMac and I've
installed Microsoft Office on it.

00:50:42.720 --> 00:50:47.120
And I moved a few things around
and that's how I want it to

00:50:47.120 --> 00:50:50.500
look for all the computers.

