So while there are very,
very few viruses for the Mac right now,

00:53:07.730 --> 00:53:12.890
there have been a couple that
are like proof of concept.

00:53:12.950 --> 00:53:14.410
There really are none in the wild.

00:53:14.520 --> 00:53:18.900
And Macs aren't affected
