00:53:35.360 --> 00:53:39.040
even though the Mac wasn't
even aware maybe that there

00:53:39.040 --> 00:53:41.220
was a virus in that message.

00:53:42.810 --> 00:53:45.560
So it's important to look at
antivirus options for the Mac and

00:53:45.560 --> 00:53:50.610
