So Disk Utility can create a disk image
that you can dump files and folders into,

00:56:06.320 --> 00:56:10.280
and that can be encrypted
at 256-bit AES encryption.

00:56:10.950 --> 00:56:13.510
And then for things like data transfers,
as Schoun touched on earlier,

00:56:13.540 --> 00:56:15.140
we've got the VPN built in.

