00:57:18.420 --> 00:57:23.080
effectively for things like pushing out
VPN certificates and stuff like that.

00:57:24.700 --> 00:57:27.570
So our strategy here is really
to understand that the antivirus

00:57:27.570 --> 00:57:30.720
options for the Mac are really not
a whole world of different from

